<codeline lineno="5"><highlight class="comment">build_prerequisites)<sp/>have<sp/>been<sp/>installed.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="6"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="7"><highlight class="comment">\section<sp/>build_gettingsrc<sp/>Getting<sp/>the<sp/>Zorba<sp/>Source<sp/>Code</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="9"><highlight class="comment">You<sp/>may<sp/>get<sp/>the<sp/>Zorba<sp/>source<sp/>code<sp/>in<sp/>one<sp/>of<sp/>two<sp/>ways:<sp/>downloading<sp/>a</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="10"><highlight class="comment">released<sp/>source<sp/>distribution,<sp/>or<sp/>getting<sp/>the<sp/>code<sp/>from<sp/>our<sp/>Launchpad</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="11"><highlight class="comment">code<sp/>repository.<sp/>The<sp/>directory<sp/>that<sp/>the<sp/>Zorba<sp/>source<sp/>code<sp/>is<sp/>placed</highlight></codeline>
